




#### To see all the modified files in a project (git)
```
Cmd+Shift+B
```


#### To fold code, script functions
```
⌘ + ⌥ + [ // To fold
⌘ + ⌥ + ] // to unfold
```

#### When typing in markdown to show the preview of the markdown
```
 ctrl(^) + shift + m
```


#### Shortcut to find commands
```
 cmd + Shift + P
```


#### To search for Files in a project
```
 ⌘ + R
```

#### To search for symbols in a files
```
 ⌘ + R
```


# Grammer

#### To search for spellings
```
 ⌘ + shift + ;
```
